  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You cannot stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You must go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then he look on me, the soldier-- I leap-- [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then I see by the third time, he can shoot me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then I step back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the third time he tell, he must go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When he show him, [GERMAN], he fell back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He shoot him straight in the head, with this leg, kick him to the road-- march.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He didn't even point with the-- with his eye.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I thought this is [SPEAKING GERMAN] murders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They can do everything like automatic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Everything, if we'll beat this Englishman, he will be nervous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "If it will be [INAUDIBLE] he will kill, he will be nervous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "If it will be a Russian, he will be nervous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He will give him a word for his mother, and his father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But the German was, from the beginning till the end, quiet, fine, with a smile, nice words, act like a beast.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "God forbid, God help us, from the cold-hearted murderers, because they can do everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The is right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My intuition was right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They will do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "This was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this gave me more than all the propaganda against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This act gave me so much hatred to see that, the world, like they show it, you see?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to escape.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I escaped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened when you went into the woods with your two friends?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we went to the woods-- but I'm in full uniform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was so afraid because when the German killed, then they will not take you the second time [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They shoot you right away, because you are on the German-- it is already German territory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they are still on the head-- on the-- on the outer worlds and that.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
